.intro:
 Pentium Processor Family Developer's Manual Volume 3: Architecture and Programming Manual
 Intel
 1995

.breakpoint.instr: The breakpoint instruction on an i386 is INT 3,
 code 0xCC.  See page 25-173.  (XREF: <URI:mut/src/arch/x86/mut_instr.h>)

.breakpoint.eip: After a trap EIP points at the instruction after the trap.
 Therefore the instruction that trapped is at EIP-1.  See section 14.9
 and 14.9.3 on pages 14-14 and 14-15. (XREF: <URI:mut/src/arch/x86/mut_pc.h>)
